# Ending scenes

=== ending_stability ===
It is not victory.

It is rent paid, bread on the table, and mornings that do not begin with panic.

=== ending_luxor ===
The train south feels unreal at first.

Luxor is not a miracle, only a place where the air loosens around your chest.

=== ending_arrested ===
The holding cell smells of heat and metal.

Somewhere above you, Cairo keeps bargaining, praying, hustling, and surviving without pause.